                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "OK, I also found a way to get back the right focus behaviour, and I think is proof that is related to *unity-window-decorator* <--> *metacity* communication. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Of course, only talking about Unity 3D.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "1) Open a lot of windows and keep them at normal size on screen (NOT maximized); some if not all, will have the wrong focus behaviour as explained extensively above. ATTENTION: do not open programs that may corrupt data if closed directly, as we are going to reboot the system trough terminal later on.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "2) Open a terminal window.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "3) Run the command \"metacity --replace\"\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "4) Entire unity interface will disappear\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "5) All windows will be replaced by metacity compositor (which anyway is already running trough unity), including window borders. Shadows will be gone.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "6) Magically, all focus behaviour will be correct now, and with the same theme in use. Of course cannot use ALT+TAB and unity launcher, top bar will be gone.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "7) To restore the system from this situation, press CTRL+ALT+T to open another terminal\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "8) Do a \"sudo reboot\" command.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "So, when unity-window-decorator is launching metacity compositor, something is wrong in there, just my 0.02$.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
